      "description": "ValidationResult produced by running the hemolysis CFD model against the FDA generic pump bench hemolysis dataset across 5 flow-speed operating points. The simulation suite was executed under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7-rc2. The release team reviewed the diff between rc2 and the final build-7 tag and concluded the two configurations are effectively the same build — only a documentation-string patch was applied — and therefore elected not to re-run the full validation suite under the released binary. Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (nIH) values agreed with experimental measurements to within ±18% across all operating points.",
