      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented release testing, regression suite, and traceable build artifacts for MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS CFX 2026-Q1 build-7 has documented release testing and a regression suite. However, the validation campaign was executed under build-7-rc2 rather than the released binary, introducing a traceability gap. SQA level assessed as 3 — version control and regression testing are present but build-artifact traceability to the validated configuration is incomplete."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and method-of-manufactured-solutions (MMS) verification for all active solver modules at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification was completed for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver and the scalar transport hemolysis damage model. Order-of-accuracy confirmed at second order spatially. Turbulence model verification limited to k-ω SST without curvature correction; full suite not completed for the hemolysis constitutive model variant used at high shear rates."
    },
    {
