      "rationale": "Numerical solver error has not been formally assessed for this COU. Residual convergence targets (RMS < 1e-5) were applied uniformly but sensitivity of nIH predictions to solver stopping criteria has not been evaluated. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
